Murillo first appeared as a [[census designated place]] under the name '''Nurillo''' in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusTX/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www2.census.gov/geo/maps/blk2000/st48_Texas/Place/4852746_Nurillo/CBP4852746_001.pdf|title=Census 2000 Block Map: Nurillo CDP|publisher=[[U.S. Census Bureau]]|access-date=2024-09-12}}</ref> The name was corrected to '''Murillo''' for the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusTX/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www2.census.gov/geo/maps/dc10map/GUBlock/st48_tx/place/p4850092_murillo/DC10BLK_P4850092_001.pdf|title=2010 Census – Census Block Map: Murillo CDP, TX|publisher=[[U.S. Census Bureau]]|access-date=2024-09-12}}</ref>

